About us

Buying & selling Harley-Davidson motorcycle parts since the 1990s, specializing in the notorious FXR! Now, it's Historical Silver pieces. Pride in my job; taking clear images, posting accurate descriptions, packaging techniques and getting your package out on schedule. Making an offer; if I accept your low offer, that means I need $$$ now, so thanks for making payment immediately. Please remember that eBay takes a bite off the top. Shipping costs; they keep going up, along with packaging materials, my overhead and everything else in America. Out of town; from time to time I leave and that means nothing gets done here. I'll let you know when I'm away. I'm the only human over here doing all the work. I won't hire someone to do these important tasks. I tried. It didn't work. That's right, I'm the guy on hands and knees packaging up your investments. I want it to get to you the same way it leaves my hands.
Thanks in advance for your business.
Sincerely,
E. of Elvis' Place (Google me)
Location: United StatesMember since: Aug 03, 1998Seller: elvis_place-hdparts
